{"type": "article", "id": 29636, "title": "海草制成的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-14T23:02:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160714220542I92ahw8X4zHKvrEW.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>提到海草，你能想象到它也可以被制成柔软的纱线、甚至是生物塑料吗？<a href=\"http://www.nienkehoogvliet.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Nienke Hoogvliet</a> 就花了两年时间对海草进行研究，希望可以将这种特殊的材料运用到设计当中，最后的成品就是由一把椅子和一个小桌组成的 <a href=\"http://www.nienkehoogvliet.nl/portfolio/sea-me-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SEA ME</a> 家具系列。为了做到零浪费，设计师们不仅用染色和晒干过程中遗留下的染料为桌子上色，还将一些剩余的废弃物制成了生物塑料碗，与桌子配套摆放。虽然 SEA ME 的两款家具的外观无法和海草联系在一起，仔细端详之后依然会发现斑驳的纤维纹路，仿佛可以闻到大海的气息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714220558rXRBdQ6MuKb2vZWw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714220558qlPOExvueFATQKL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714220558VxWpI1RtiL8sFwqe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714220559SyObXtk6AarMgphE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}